title: Gucci Mane Wrote the Autobiography
description:
Welcome to The Autobiography of Gucci Mane. From the birth of trap music to face tattoos, Gucci leaves almost nothing out.  Except the parts he has to (for legal reasons) or can't remember (for other reasons). This week Claire and Ashley get a crash course in the Atlanta scene.


Tees are Here!! Grab a Worm Tee or an Unhinged Tee here: https://celebritymemoirbookclub.square.site/

If you want even more juice subscribe to our patreon!!! https://www.patreon.com/celebritymemoirbookclub
